<h1>Bayesian Integrative Genomics</h1>
<h4>Phase I: Funded by the BBSRC <a href="http://www.bbsrc.ac.uk/science/initiatives/exploiting_genomics.html">Exploiting Genomics</a> initiative, from May 2002 to February 2007.</h4>
<h4>Phase II: A collaborative programme started in 2008, coordinated by <a href="https://www1.imperial.ac.uk/medicine/people/sylvia.richardson/">Prof Sylvia Richardson</a>.</h4>
</div>
